---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Download" description="Download and install TAOM - Tales From the Age of Men for Bannerlord">
  <div class="page-content" style="max-width: 850px;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Download & Install</h1>

    <div class="card alert-card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Compatibility</h3>
      <p><strong>This mod is compatible with Bannerlord 1.2.12 through Steam.</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>You will need to roll your game back to version 1.2.12.</li>
        <li>This mod <strong>cannot</strong> be used with the Xbox Game Pass version of the game.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Be sure to delete any old files of the mod you may have downloaded before starting the process of a new download.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Video Tutorial</h3>
      <p>For a video walkthrough of the install process:</p>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cu7K5skn2Fo" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch on YouTube</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Option 1: Launcher (Recommended)</h3>
      <p>Download the launcher for automatic installation and updates:</p>
      <a href="https://lotraom.com/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Download Launcher</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Option 2: Manual Download</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Download the latest release from one of these sources:</p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <a href="https://www.moddb.com/mods/tales-from-the-age-of-men" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ModDB</a>
        <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/mountandblade2bannerlord/mods/7748" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nexus Mods</a>
      </div>
      <p class="note">The most recent public release is dated January 1st.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Manual Installation Steps</h3>
      <ol class="install-steps">
        <li>
          <strong>Download</strong> the mod from ModDB or Nexus Mods (2 files from Nexus).
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Extract</strong> the downloaded files using WinRAR, 7zip, or similar.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Open your Modules folder:</strong>
          <code class="code-block">
            Steam\steamapps\common\Mount & Blade II Bannerlord\Modules\
          </code>
          <span class="note">Your drive letter may vary — check wherever Bannerlord is installed.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Delete old files</strong> from any previous versions of the mod in your Modules folder.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Copy files</strong> — Open the extracted folder, select all files within it, and drag them into the Modules folder.
          <span class="note">We provide every file you need, including dependencies.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Unblock DLLs</strong> — Right-click each DLL file → Properties → check "Unblock", or run this PowerShell command in the Modules folder:
          <code class="code-block">
            Get-ChildItem -Recurse -Filter *.dll | Unblock-File
          </code>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Delete shaders</strong> if you played this mod before:
          <code class="code-block">
            C:\ProgramData\Mount and Blade II Bannerlord\Shaders\TerrainShaders\LOTR_Map
          </code>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <h3>Load Order</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><strong>Bannerlord Version 1.2.12</strong> — Set this exact load order in the launcher:</p>
      <ol class="load-order">
        <li><span class="mod-name">Harmony</span> <span class="mod-version">v2.3.6.220</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Palantir Debugger</span> <span class="mod-note">Writes crash logs for diagnostics</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">BetterExceptionWindow</span> <span class="mod-version">v7.1.1.0</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">ButterLib</span> <span class="mod-version">v2.10.0.0</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">UIExtenderEx</span> <span class="mod-version">v2.13.0.0</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">MCM</span> <span class="mod-version">v5.11.3.0</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Native</span> <span class="mod-version">1.2.12.X</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Sandbox Core</span> <span class="mod-version">1.2.12.X</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Sandbox</span> <span class="mod-version">1.2.12.X</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">StoryMode</span> <span class="mod-version">1.2.12.X</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">CustomBattle</span> <span class="mod-version">1.2.12.X</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Birth and Aging Options</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">LOTR_Map</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">LOTRAOM_Armory</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name">Alliance.Wargs</span></li>
        <li><span class="mod-name highlight">LOTRAOM</span> <span class="mod-version highlight">v0.69.3</span></li>
      </ol>
      <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Press <strong>Play</strong>, then go to Options and set <strong>Terrain Quality</strong> to Medium or higher.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
      <div class="troubleshoot-item">
        <p><strong>"Cannot load" a DLL file?</strong></p>
        <p>Unblock the DLL files manually using PowerShell. Run the unblock command from step 6 above. If PowerShell returns with a new blank line, it was done correctly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="troubleshoot-item">
        <p><strong>Main loading screen frozen (horse not moving)?</strong></p>
        <p>This is normal — let it load. The initial load can take a while.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="troubleshoot-item">
        <p><strong>Still having issues?</strong></p>
        <p>Join our Discord for help and support.</p>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/taom" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join Discord</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="community-badges">
      <div class="badge-block">
        <p class="badge-label">To follow the development of the mod, check out the development blogs on</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@haterade_industries" class="badge-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="/images/youtube-badge.svg" alt="YouTube" class="badge-img" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="badge-block">
        <p class="badge-label">For more information about the mod, assistance, or to interact with the development team</p>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/taom" class="badge-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="/images/discord-badge.svg" alt="Join the Chat on Discord" class="badge-img" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .alert-card {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .alert-card ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .install-steps {
    list-style: decimal;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .install-steps li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .code-block {
    display: block;
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .note {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .load-order {
    list-style: decimal;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .load-order li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .mod-name {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .mod-version {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .mod-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .mod-name.highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .mod-version.highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .troubleshoot-item {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .troubleshoot-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .community-badges {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .badge-block {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .badge-label {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .badge-link {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s, filter 0.2s;
  }

  .badge-link:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    filter: brightness(1.1);
  }

  .badge-img {
    height: 55px;
    width: auto;
  }
</style>
